│ 2176 // relaxed in the future.                                                │
│ 2177 // Please, note that we are currently forced to abuse the pragma 'clang  │
│ 2178 // vectorize' semantics. This pragma provides *auto-vectorization hints* │
│ 2179 // (i.e., LV must check that vectorization is legal) whereas pragma 'omp │
│ simd'                                                                         │
│ 2180 // provides *explicit vectorization hints* (LV can bypass legal checks   │
│ and                                                                           │
│ 2181 // assume that vectorization is legal). However, both hints are          │
│ implemented                                                                   │
